## Rule for implementation

Do not solve future-day scope prematurely unless explicitly asked.

Example:
- Day 15 should prepare Day 16, not fully implement Day 16
- Day 17 should improve custom-fields usability, not redesign import
- Day 18 should polish product UX, not jump into orders

## Sign-off rule

When asked to verify completion:
- distinguish core functional completion vs sign-off readiness
- do not mark a day done if major merchant workflow residue remains